Usage: deleteWhatIfTimingAssertions [-help] [<blackBoxCellName>]
                                    [-assertion_type {setup comb hold}] [-rising  | -falling ] [-port <portName> | [-from <from> -to <to>] | -from <from> | -to <to>]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxCellName>                    # name of the blackbox or blackblob cell
                                      # (string, optional)
-assertion_type {setup comb hold}     # Specifies one of the following
                                      # assertion types (enum, optional)
-falling                              # Specifies that timing arcs should be
                                      # deleted for falling clock transitions
                                      # (bool, optional)
-from <from>                          # Specifies all arcs starting from the
                                      # port  (string, optional)
-port <portName>                      # Specifies the name of one or more ports
                                      # (string, optional)
-rising                               # Specifies that timing arcs should be
                                      # deleted for rising clock transitions
                                      # (bool, optional)
-to <to>                              # Specifies all arcs ending at the port 
                                      # (string, optional)